# Title: Potential Credential Dumping Attempt Via PowerShell Remote Thread
# Author: oscd.community, Natalia Shornikova
# Date: 2020-10-06
# Level: high
# Description: Detects remote thread creation by PowerShell processes into "lsass.exe"
# MITRE Tactic: Credential Access
# Tags: attack.credential-access, attack.t1003.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/create_remote_thread/create_remote_thread_win_powershell_lsass.yml

SourceImage IN ("*\\powershell.exe", "*\\pwsh.exe") TargetImage="*\\lsass.exe"